CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Western New England Bancorp Inc is a chartered stock holding company and the parent company of Westfield Bank. The company through its subsidiaries provides banking products and services offering a variety of deposit products and makes mortgage loans for the construction, purchase, and refinancing of residential and commercial real estate as well as other commercial and consumer loans of various types.
